{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c162f2e6d","title":"七绝·改梅白《夜登重庆批把山","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45896d386d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"4c162f2e6d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"6ba8112ba1","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4c162f2e6d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"年，毛泽东视察三峡，梅白跟随在他身边。毛泽东见梅白写的一首七绝《夜登重庆机把山》，颜有兴致，就对梅白的诗做了修改。主要有以下几处：（1）苍范，原诗为辉煌。（2）百万，原诗为几万。（3）摇倒影，原诗为流倒影。（4）似，原诗为比。"}],"contents":[{"id":"28c774012e","type":"title","text":"七绝·改梅白《夜登重庆批把山》叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4c162f2e6d"},{"id":"6ba8112ba1","type":"paragraph","text":"我来高处欲乘风，暮色苍范一望中。百万银灯摇倒影，嘉陵江似水晶宫。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4c162f2e6d"}],"page":{"id":"c3b49feeb6","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4c162f2e6d","start":162,"end":162}}}},"__N_SSG":true}